quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  4,105,"Nabiyow Diggah nanu Qhuraan kitab cakkil kol oobisne, Yalli wacyih kol oobiseeh koo yuybulleemil Sinam fan mekeltamkeh, sinni nafsi cakki yaaqureenimit ganah yan marah (tuqma deqsita numih mara kinnuk) cato makkinaay keenih mahawsin"
  4,106,"Nabiyow Yallak dambi cabti esserit, Diggah Yalli dambi cabti- li xuwawli kinnik"
  4,107,"sinni nafsi Yallih amrih cinat ganah yan mara macatinaay ken Afak mayaabin, Diggah Yalli gano kak nabaah dambi kak maggo mara mayakcinak"
  4,108,"Usun uma taamoomi keenik yableenimik Sinaamak yambooqoreeniih Yallak mayambooqoran usuk ken luk anuk, isi ixxigah ken caalat yaaxigeh Bar yaabak Yalli edde leede waa uma malat xiinan waqdi, Yallih ixxiga umman ken maxcoocaa kee ken uma taamoomiy abba haanat maroh tan"
  4,109,"Moominiiney isin Amah siini Ama marah (tuqma deqsita numih mara kinnuk) Addunyâ manol hawissaanaah keenih Sumaaqittaanahak, tokkel Qhiyaamah ayró Ama gano abak Yallih digaala iyyi waase-lee? hinnak Abba iyyi keenik Akkeleeh iyyi ken cate-lee"
  4,110,"Umaah Qaxumaane-le taamat Aseeh hinnay Yallih Amrih cinat isi nafsi yudlumeh yan num, tohuk lakal Yalla dambi cabti esserek, Yalla dambi cabti-li xuwaw-lih kaa geele"
  4,111,"dambi loowitik abeh yan num, toysa usuk cagalah isi nafsi dambi elle orbisam, Yalli isi naqoosah caagiida yaaxigi keenih madqeemil Naggaar kinni"
  4,112,"num Qunxa dambi Abek hinnay kaxxa dambi abek, tohuk lakal dambik Barih yan numul kaa Qidek, toysa Nummah usuk dirab kee ereriiy Baxxaqqa iyya dambi yussukuqqeh"